page.title: 09GRID SQUARE NINE
page.content: There is not really much in this grid other than fields and woods but there is a 4.3 metres metalled road and a survey of the traffic which past on a 1 hour survey is as follows _ 2_12 year old cars, 2_11 year old cars, 2_10 year old cars,3_9 year old cars, 1_8 year old car, 5_7 year old cars,5_6 year old cars, 5_5 year old cars, 2_4 year old cars, 5_3 year old cars and 2 were 2 year old cars. In the fields nearby the crops are 28% cereal, 40% grazing, 10% are root crops and 22% is woodland. Overall this is a very desolate grid square.
